    "introHtml": "<p>Top 10 picks for a cheap fun second car near Media, PA (ZIP 19063) — ranked by condition, reliability, and fun factor. All picks confirmed available on AutoTrader page 1 today. Notable price drops this run: 2007 MINI Cooper S ($9,500→$8,452), 1992 Chevrolet Corvette ($11,500→$9,500). New listing: 2009 Saturn Sky (22K mi). Chrome unavailable — Cars.com and CarGurus listings not retrieved.</p>",
