        "source": "autotrader",
        "url": "https://www.autotrader.com/cars-for-sale/vehicle/775917821",
        "whyGood": "The Z3 2.8 gets the rare inline-6 (M52B28) that makes this roadster genuinely fun to drive — not just cute. $7,940, 75K miles, No Accidents, clean title via Private Seller Exchange, only 14.81 mi away. Price-to-fun ratio is unbeatable in this market. The 2.8L smooth six is a step-change over the base 1.9 four.",
        "whatToVerify": "Operate soft top through a full open-close cycle; check headliner and carpet for water staining; inspect rear plastic window for yellowing or delamination; look at rocker panels and front frame rails for rust; check cooling system (thermostat, water pump — M52 runs hot when neglected); VANOS rattle on cold start; valve cover gasket seep.",
        "bottomLine": "Best-value fun roadster in the pool — inline-6 Z3 at a great price with clean history."
      },
      {
        "rank": 2,
